<center> Email Auto Responder</center>
<hr>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
	Allow your users to create<i> email auto responders </i>which reply to the sender of incoming mail with a preset message. <br>
<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
		Check the<i> Include </i>box to make this resource available under the plan. Later you can define the amount of auto responders a user can create for free, its setup and recurrent fee.<br>